steps.name: launch the widget browser with the valid token
ensure your on the purpose Of Visit Page
select one card and click on the continue button
ensure your on the preference Page
select the OHR card and click on the continue button
upload images from your local space and click on result button
ensure you are on the contact info page
fill all the necessary information and click on the submit button
